        "subject": "LU-3166 build: Fix failed OFED even checking on OFED-3.5",
        "message": "LU-3166 build: Fix failed OFED even checking on OFED-3.5\n\nFrom: http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6048/\ncompat driver's header for OFED-3.5 is missing to check\nwhether OFED events are defined in OFED-3.5.\n\nFrom: http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6448/5\nOFED-3.5.1 supports RHEL6.4 kernel. CONFIG_COMPAT_RHEL_6_4 macro\nneeds to build lustre with them.\n\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <minh.diep@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I98a83248accde062984651835ae9fd899e533657\n"
      },
